{"tid":2101784,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"福建幫被捕後向警掟飯盒 認罪辯稱「餓得太耐」今判感化","createTime":"2020-07-10T04:47:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-10T04:58:32.000Z","uid":60281,"like":5,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"43a8e5e4c53e57e5a16c8feeb54ad79ab2989f01","tid":2101784,"uid":60281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T04:47:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n去年9月有遊行人士到港島「行街」，當晚北角有多宗「福建幫」與示威者衝突事件。其中「福建幫」邱宗源因涉嫌管有攻擊性武器被捕，其間自稱不適，要求送院。及後他在醫院內欲進食親友帶來的飯盒時，遭警員阻止，遂以飯盒掟向警員。他早前原本被控襲警罪，及後獲改控普通襲擊罪，並且認罪，求情指因「餓得太耐」，一時失控犯案。裁判官接納他只是一時衝動犯案，判他接受感化一年。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200710/ZZEBW6GD6ITWND3OI444KSYSTI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200710%2FZZEBW6GD6ITWND3OI444KSYSTI%2F&d=gCjj53haX7oQ0UVj6qLsjsyZng7V5AOcQmv89xdKlzQ%3D&h=fe9de8da\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200710%2FZZEBW6GD6ITWND3OI444KSYSTI%2F&h=6d6812e6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200710/ZZEBW6GD6ITWND3OI444KSYSTI/</a>"},{"pid":"057b92bfae323d0211afa72a3e46bb0e4c26d60d","tid":2101784,"uid":46906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T04:49:07.000Z","msg":"攻擊性武器果單呢"},{"pid":"eed7e7c49237405bda337386c05298b7598c0066","tid":2101784,"uid":14454,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T04:50:11.000Z","msg":"感化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05bcb6b8a75c00d2d0bd4081321f4fb21b775cfa","tid":2101784,"uid":121197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T04:51:28.000Z","msg":"咁曾志偉向黃秋生潑飯盒要判啲咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"482b082b943f8aa4a6216b66ff00273a4ca5d4fa","tid":2101784,"uid":51271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T04:52:28.000Z","msg":"點解唔告